# Cookie Awareness Website

## Description
A simple React-based website for cookie awareness and GDPR compliance. It includes a cookie banner, user consent options, and a detailed cookie policy page.

## Prerequisites
- Node.js >= 16.x
- npm >= 8.x

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-repo/cookie-awareness.git
   ```
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

